<ce:inf loc="post">NN</ce:inf>, <ce:italic>δ</ce:italic>
<ce:inf loc="post">NNN</ce:inf> and <ce:italic>δ</ce:italic>
<ce:inf loc="post">c</ce:inf> are fitting variables. Assuming a perfectly random distribution of Ti atoms, and we write the model lineshape as:<ce:display>
